Info.description: Interne at Allied Group of Consultants
Info.about: Shaheen loves to connect with learning enthusiasts and solve problems. She gains inspiration and insight through thought-provoking productive discussions. She's naturally an inquisitive lifetime learner and enjoys keeping up with current happenings in related technologies, she believes that mentoring is so deeply satisfying job/service that helps to fulfill her knowledge sharing desire and stay motivated to fuel her life long learning enthusiasm by learning/sharing along with mentees.
